      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把主干画出来：DRAFT通过publish到OPEN，OPEN可以pause到PAUSED，也能close without fill直接到CLOSED。草稿也能直接archive。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DRAFT",
